description:
Twoo is the most fun way to meet new people in your area on your iOS device.

Millions of people
With over 10 million active people, Twoo is the largest community of its kind in the world!

Real people, really active
Every day, over a million people connect with each other on Twoo. Whether you fancy chatting, searching, sharing photos or playing our fun introductory games, Twoo is full of exciting new people to have fun with, and maybe even to meet.

"I recently moved to Amsterdam from London. Twoo made it easy to create a social circle in minutes! It’s SO much fun talking to new people and learning how to make new friends, easily!" Peter – Amsterdam

"Twoo is super cool on mobile. I can choose who I speak to and who speaks to me." Boris, Bremen

"There’s always loads of great people online." Louis – São Paulo

Twoo is free to download and use, but you can enjoy extra features thanks to Twoo Unlimited or boost your popularity with Twoo Credits.

- Payments will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.
- You can choose between a weekly (€3.59), monthly (€9.99), three-monthly (€24.99), six-monthly (€39.99) or yearly (€69.99) Twoo Unlimited subscription (prices can vary depending on your country).
- You can manage your subscription or stop automatic renewal at any time through the Settings of your account.
- Your subscription will automatically renew, unless you have cancelled at the latest 24 hours before the end of the current period.
- After cancelling your subscription, your subscription will remain active until the end of the purchased period.
- Free trial period expires completely once you have purchased a subscription.
- Privacy policy: http://www.twoo.com/about/privacy
- Terms & conditions: http://www.twoo.com/about/terms
releaseNotes: We've been working a lot on improving our app. We made sure you can enjoy the best Twoo experience by making a faster and smoother app.
